@startuml
title Scrumlr.io - Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Frontend\n(React/Redux)" as Frontend
participant "API Router\n(router.go)" as Router
participant "Auth Middleware\n(auth.go)" as Auth
participant "API Handler" as Handler
participant "Service Layer\n(boards/notes/users)" as Service
participant "Database\n(bun ORM)" as Database
participant "Realtime\n(NATS/Redis)" as Realtime
participant "WebSocket\nConnection" as WebSocket

== User Authentication ==
User -> Frontend: Navigate to board
Frontend -> Router: GET /api/boards/{id}
Router -> Auth: Authenticate request
Auth -> Auth: Validate token/session
Auth -> Router: Authentication result
Router -> Handler: Forward authenticated request
Handler -> Service: GetBoard(boardID)
Service -> Database: Query board data
Database -> Service: Return board
Service -> Handler: Board DTO
Handler -> Router: HTTP Response (Board data)
Router -> Frontend: Board JSON
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Update board state
Frontend -> User: Display board

== Establish WebSocket Connection ==
Frontend -> WebSocket: Connect to /boards/{id}/listen
WebSocket -> Auth: Authenticate WebSocket
Auth -> WebSocket: Connection authorized
WebSocket -> Realtime: Subscribe to board events
Realtime -> WebSocket: Subscription confirmed
WebSocket -> Frontend: Connection established

== Create Note ==
User -> Frontend: Create new note
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Dispatch createNote action
Frontend -> Router: POST /api/boards/{id}/notes
Router -> Auth: Verify authorization
Auth -> Router: Authorized
Router -> Handler: CreateNote handler
Handler -> Service: CreateNote(boardID, noteData)
Service -> Database: Insert note record
Database -> Service: Note created
Service -> Realtime: Publish NOTE_CREATED event
Service -> Handler: Note DTO
Handler -> Router: HTTP 201 Created
Router -> Frontend: Note JSON
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Add note to state
Frontend -> User: Display new note

== Real-time Update Propagation ==
Realtime -> WebSocket: NOTE_CREATED event
WebSocket -> WebSocket: Filter event for board
WebSocket -> Frontend: Push event data
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Update state
Frontend -> User: Update UI (other users see note)

== Vote on Note ==
User -> Frontend: Click vote on note
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Dispatch vote action
Frontend -> Router: POST /api/boards/{id}/votes
Router -> Auth: Verify authorization
Auth -> Router: Authorized
Router -> Handler: CreateVote handler
Handler -> Service: CreateVote(noteID, userID)
Service -> Database: Insert vote record
Database -> Service: Vote created
Service -> Realtime: Publish VOTE_CREATED event
Service -> Handler: Vote DTO
Handler -> Router: HTTP 201 Created
Router -> Frontend: Vote JSON
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Update vote state
Frontend -> User: Update vote count

Realtime -> WebSocket: VOTE_CREATED event
WebSocket -> Frontend: Push vote event
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Update state
Frontend -> User: Sync vote count

== Update Note (Stack/Edit) ==
User -> Frontend: Edit note content
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Dispatch updateNote
Frontend -> Router: PUT /api/boards/{id}/notes/{noteId}
Router -> Auth: Verify authorization
Auth -> Router: Authorized
Router -> Handler: UpdateNote handler
Handler -> Service: UpdateNote(noteID, updates)
Service -> Database: Update note record
Database -> Service: Note updated
Service -> Realtime: Publish NOTE_UPDATED event
Service -> Handler: Updated note DTO
Handler -> Router: HTTP 200 OK
Router -> Frontend: Updated note JSON
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Update note state
Frontend -> User: Display updated note

Realtime -> WebSocket: NOTE_UPDATED event
WebSocket -> Frontend: Push update event
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Sync state
Frontend -> User: Reflect changes

== User Session Management ==
Frontend -> Router: POST /api/boards/{id}/sessions
Router -> Auth: Verify authorization
Auth -> Router: Authorized
Router -> Handler: CreateSession handler
Handler -> Service: CreateSession(boardID, userID)
Service -> Database: Insert session record
Database -> Service: Session created
Service -> Realtime: Publish SESSION_JOINED event
Service -> Handler: Session DTO
Handler -> Router: HTTP 201 Created
Router -> Frontend: Session JSON
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Add user session

Realtime -> WebSocket: SESSION_JOINED event
WebSocket -> Frontend: Push session event
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Update users state
Frontend -> User: Show user joined

== Export Board Data ==
User -> Frontend: Request board export
Frontend -> Router: GET /api/boards/{id}/export?format=json
Router -> Auth: Verify authorization
Auth -> Router: Authorized
Router -> Handler: ExportBoard handler
Handler -> Service: ExportBoard(boardID, format)
Service -> Database: Query all board data
Database -> Service: Board, columns, notes, votes
Service -> Service: Transform to export format
Service -> Handler: Export data
Handler -> Router: HTTP 200 with file
Router -> Frontend: Download response
Frontend -> User: Download file

== Delete Note ==
User -> Frontend: Delete note
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Dispatch deleteNote
Frontend -> Router: DELETE /api/boards/{id}/notes/{noteId}
Router -> Auth: Verify authorization
Auth -> Router: Authorized
Router -> Handler: DeleteNote handler
Handler -> Service: DeleteNote(noteID)
Service -> Database: Delete note record
Database -> Service: Note deleted
Service -> Realtime: Publish NOTE_DELETED event
Service -> Handler: Success response
Handler -> Router: HTTP 204 No Content
Router -> Frontend: Success
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Remove note
Frontend -> User: Note removed from UI

Realtime -> WebSocket: NOTE_DELETED event
WebSocket -> Frontend: Push delete event
Frontend -> Frontend: Redux: Sync deletion
Frontend -> User: Update UI

== WebSocket Disconnect ==
User -> Frontend: Leave board/close tab
Frontend -> WebSocket: Close connection
WebSocket -> Realtime: Unsubscribe from events
Realtime -> WebSocket: Unsubscribed
WebSocket -> Frontend: Connection closed

@enduml
